org.wisepersist.gwt.uploader.client.events

Class AbstractUploadEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wisepersist.gwt.uploader.client.events.AbstractUploadEvent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UploadCompleteEvent, UploadErrorEvent, UploadProgressEvent, UploadStartEvent, UploadSuccessEvent

    public abstract class AbstractUploadEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class of all events that are triggered during the uploader process, and includes methods for accessing the general state of the event, most notably the details of the file that is being uploaded.
